    "For each of them, we run ATLA by setting maximum forward budget as 200 to attack LLAMA2-7B-CHAT.",
    "Then we feed the generated responses into an evaluation system to determine the minimum required budget for a success attack.",
    "Besides the human-involved evaluation system, we also use two powerful commercial LLMs, GPT-4-preview and GPT-4, as our evaluators.",
    "To improve the accuracy of the evaluation, we set the system prompt as in Table. 9.",
    "We visualize the distributions of ASR with respect to the forward budget evaluated with different judgement systems in Fig. 7."
